- Support LF and LFCR line ends
  (needs fgets() alternative).

- remove -n input mode,
  add its functionality (column aliasing) to -a mode,
  have "-n" option as legacy alias for "-U -a" (with coldef requirement)

- Support --filter:
  drop all records which contain only empty fields

- Support --filter-mode for --filter:
    - none    (same as omitting --filter entirely)
    - all-empty | z (default)
    - all-zero | 0
    - all-empty-or-zero | z0 | 0z		-- Drop all records which contain only empty and/or "0" fields

